# │ G-LANG: 0010 ERR: 0001 LAT: 35ms ROUTES: 3            │
# │ HEALTH: [████████████████████████░] 90%                │
# │                                                         │
# │ > _                                                     │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
#
# Token count: ~18 tokens for full backend health
# vs 2400+ tokens for equivalent JSON logs
# Efficiency: 133x faster context processing
